data.description: Attention All Medical Providers! Last of its kind in the Jacksonville Market area under $1,200,000. Located only 2 Miles from the Baptist Clay Medical Campus Hospital. Riverfront flag lot 1.1+ acres in private Hibernia Plantation! This luxurious, all-brick custom beauty was designed with quality, security & future technology in mind! 4 car garage w/ HVAC. Fully-equipped Media Room w/ 125'' HD Projection, plush theater seating & its own wet bar. Top of the line Kitchen includes GE Monogram Appliances, Convention/Convection & Advantium Ovens, granite, butler pantry & custom cabinetry. Super energy efficient. 3 Gas fireplaces, solar tubes, 15KW LP Generator. 4th BR used as office w/ custom built-ins. High and dry 12+ ft. Please see Additional  Features under Documents tab
